<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
With the [[Image:Assembly_CreateAssembly.svg|24px]] [[Assembly_CreateAssembly|Create Assembly]] tool add an assembly to the document.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
